or stress relief.<br></li><li><strong>Embrace the Challenge:</strong> Seek out tougher quests and obstacles to push your skills and customize your experience.<br></li><li><strong>Futuristic Setting:</strong> Explore impressive, modern cities and dive into a sci-fi atmosphere.<br></li><li><strong>Visually Stunning:</strong> Enjoy breathtaking stylized graphics and a unique cityscape.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073760/extras/93063b9dc977f40016f44f15ebfe4c54.poster.avif?t=1761329093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073760/extras/93063b9dc977f40016f44f15ebfe4c54.webm?t=1761329093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073760/extras/93063b9dc977f40016f44f15ebfe4c54.mp4?t=1761329093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer the Horizon</h2>Get ready for the ultimate parkour experience in &quot;Glass Horizon&quot; and show the world what you're made of. Are you ready to conquer the horizon?",
